{"id":49,"parent_id":30,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":49,"title":"2 Nephi 19","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Ne.","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 19"],[".studySummary",["i","Isaiah speaks messianically—The people in darkness will see a great light—Unto us a child is born—He will be the Prince of Peace and will reign on David’s throne—Compare",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/9"},"Isaiah 9"],". About 559–545",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.1","order":"05.13.019.5218"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Nevertheless"],", the dimness shall not be such as was in her vexation, when at first he lightly afflicted the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"land"],"of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"Zebulun"],", and the land of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"Naphtali"],", and afterwards did more grievously afflict by the way of the Red Sea beyond Jordan in Galilee of the nations."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.2","order":"05.13.019.5219"},["b","2"],"The people that walked in darkness have seen a great light; they that dwell in the land of the shadow of death, upon them hath the light shined."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.3","order":"05.13.019.5220"},["b","3"],"Thou hast multiplied the nation, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"increased"],"the joy—they joy before thee according to the joy in harvest, and as men rejoice when they divide the spoil."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.4","order":"05.13.019.5221"},["b","4"],"For thou hast broken the yoke of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"his"],"burden, and the staff of his shoulder, the rod of his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"oppressor"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.5","order":"05.13.019.5222"},["b","5"],"For every battle of the warrior is with confused noise, and garments rolled in blood; but",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"this"],"shall be with burning and fuel of fire."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.6","order":"05.13.019.5223"},["b","6"],"For unto us a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"child"],"is born, unto us a son is given; and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"government"],"shall be upon his shoulder; and his name shall be called, Wonderful, Counselor, The",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"Mighty God"],", The",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_6d"},"Everlasting Father"],", The Prince of",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_6e"},"Peace"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.7","order":"05.13.019.5224"},["b","7"],"Of the increase of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"government"],"and peace",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"there"],"is no end, upon the throne of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"David"],", and upon his kingdom to order it, and to establish it with judgment and with justice from henceforth, even forever. The zeal of the Lord of Hosts will perform this."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.8","order":"05.13.019.5225"},["b","8"],"The Lord sent his word unto Jacob and it hath lighted upon Israel."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.9","order":"05.13.019.5226"},["b","9"],"And all the people shall know, even Ephraim and the inhabitants of Samaria, that say in the pride and stoutness of heart:"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.10","order":"05.13.019.5227"},["b","10"],"The bricks are fallen down, but we will build with hewn",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"stones"],"; the sycamores are cut down, but we will change them into",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"cedars"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.11","order":"05.13.019.5228"},["b","11"],"Therefore the Lord shall set up the adversaries of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Rezin"],"against him, and join his enemies together;"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.12","order":"05.13.019.5229"},["b","12"],"The Syrians before and the Philistines behind; and they shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"devour"],"Israel with open mouth. For all this his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"anger"],"is not turned away, but his hand is stretched out still."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.13","order":"05.13.019.5230"},["b","13"],"For the people turneth not unto",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"him"],"that smiteth them, neither do they seek the Lord of Hosts."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.14","order":"05.13.019.5231"},["b","14"],"Therefore will the Lord cut off from Israel head and tail, branch and rush",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"in"],"one day."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.15","order":"05.13.019.5232"},["b","15"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"ancient"],", he is the head; and the prophet that teacheth lies, he is the tail."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.16","order":"05.13.019.5233"},["b","16"],"For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"leaders"],"of this people cause them to err; and they that are",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"led"],"of them are destroyed."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.17","order":"05.13.019.5234"},["b","17"],"Therefore the Lord shall have no joy in their young men, neither shall have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"mercy"],"on their fatherless and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"widows"],"; for",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"every"],"one of them is a hypocrite and an",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_17d"},"evildoer"],", and every mouth speaketh",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_17e"},"folly"],". For all this his anger is not turned away, but his",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_17f"},"hand"],"is stretched out still."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.18","order":"05.13.019.5235"},["b","18"],"For",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"wickedness"],"burneth as the fire; it shall devour the briers and thorns, and shall kindle in the thickets of the forests, and they shall mount up like the lifting up of smoke."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.19","order":"05.13.019.5236"},["b","19"],"Through the wrath of the Lord of Hosts is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"land"],"darkened, and the people shall be as the fuel of the fire;",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"no man"],"shall spare his brother."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.20","order":"05.13.019.5237"},["b","20"],"And he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"shall"],"snatch on the right hand and be hungry; and he shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"eat"],"on the left hand and they shall not be satisfied; they shall eat every man the flesh of his own arm—"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.21","order":"05.13.019.5238"},["b","21"],"Manasseh,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"Ephraim"],"; and Ephraim, Manasseh; they together shall be against",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"Judah"],". For all this his anger is not turned away, but his hand is stretched out still."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.1a","order":"05.13.019.5239"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/9.1.1-21"},"Isa. 9:1 (1–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.1b","order":"05.13.019.5241"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/4.15.15-16"},"Matt. 4:15 (15–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.1c","order":"05.13.019.5243"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/19.10.10-16"},"Josh. 19:10 (10–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.1d","order":"05.13.019.5245"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/19.33.32-39"},"Josh. 19:33 (32–39)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.3a","order":"05.13.019.5247"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/9.3"},"Isa. 9:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.4a","order":"05.13.019.5249"},["b","4a"],["span.small","IE"],"Israel, the nation mentioned in",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.3"},"v. 3"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.4b","order":"05.13.019.5251"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/oppression"},"TG Oppression"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.5a","order":"05.13.019.5253"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/4.1"},"Mal. 4:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.6a","order":"05.13.019.5255"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/7.14"},"Isa. 7:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/2.11"},"Luke 2:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.6b","order":"05.13.019.5257"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.18"},"Matt. 28:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.6c","order":"05.13.019.5259"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/titus/2.13"},"Titus 2:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/7.27"},"Mosiah 7:27"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-jehovah"},"TG Jesus Christ, Jehovah"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-power-of"},"Jesus Christ, Power of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.6d","order":"05.13.019.5261"},["b","6d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/26.12"},"2 Ne. 26:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.5"},"Mosiah 3:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/11.39.38-39,44"},"Alma 11:39 (38–39, 44)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/7.22"},"Moro. 7:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/8.18"},"8:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"6e","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.6e","order":"05.13.019.5263"},